<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.4.7">
<l>paiviriyum variyaravil paṭukaṭaluḷ tuyilamarnta paṇpā veṉṟum</l>
<l>maiviriyum maṇivaraipōl māyavaṉē yeṉṟeṉṟum vaṇṭār nīlam</l>
<l>ceyviriyun taṇcēṟai yemperumāṉ tiruvaṭiyai cintit tēṟkeṉ</l>
<l>aiyaṟivuṅ koṇṭāṉuk kāḷāṉārk kāḷāme ṉaṉpu tāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Saying, “[You of] quality who rests in repose in the crashing sea</l>
<l rend="indent">on a striped serpent with heads spread,</l>
<l>And always saying, “Māyavaṉ like a jeweled mountain</l>
<l rend="indent">where dark [clouds] spread,”</l>
<l>For me, who meditates on the divine feet of our great lord of cool Cēṟai</l>
<l rend="indent">where fields spread with waterlilies where bees hum,</l>
<l>My love is a servant to those who became servants to him</l>
<l rend="indent">who captivated my five senses.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
